      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Weekly business report\nEvery Monday 8am: new leads, new intakes, open tickets, and website visits from the last 7 days — one email, plain English.\n\n### Setup\n1. In ALL THREE 'Get…' nodes, replace PASTE_SERVICE_KEY (both headers each) with your Supabase service_role key.\n2. Attach your email credential on the Email node.\n3. Save → flip **Active**.",
